prompt: Hi
completion: Hi! How can I assist you today?

prompt: What is your pricing?
completion: Our pricing starts at $99 per month. For details, visit '/dashboard/pricing'.

prompt: How do I see my order details?
completion: Go to '/yourorder/detailorder' from the dashboard to see your order details.

prompt: Can you recommend a plan for a small business?
completion: Sure! For small businesses, our Starter Plan is a great fit. You can review its features at '/dashboard/pricing'.

prompt: How do I add a new website?
completion: To add a new website, click 'Add Website' on your dashboard or go to '/dashboard/addwebsite'.

prompt: Can I filter websites by domain rating?
completion: Yes, use the Domain Rating slider in the filter panel to select your preferred range.

prompt: What does 'Exclude Existing Domains & IPs' mean?
completion: This filter lets you exclude domains and IPs you already own or have purchased from your search results.

prompt: How do I change the currency for prices?
completion: You can change the currency by selecting your preferred option in the Currency dropdown in the filter panel.

prompt: I can't find the group filter
completion: The Group filter is under the 'Exclude Existing Domains & IPs' section. If you need help, visit '/dashboard/help'.

prompt: Can you recommend a website for backlinks?
completion: Sure! Please specify your niche or target country, and I'll suggest relevant websites for backlinks.

prompt: What is the difference between Permanent Article and Yearly Article?
completion: A Permanent Article stays on the website indefinitely, while a Yearly Article is published for one year and may be removed afterward.

prompt: How do I reset my password?
completion: Click 'Forgot Password' on the login page or go to '/auth/resetpassword' and follow the instructions.

prompt: Can I export my website list?
completion: Yes, click the 'Export' button at the top of the website table or go to '/dashboard/export'.

prompt: The filter panel is not responsive on my phone
completion: Sorry for the inconvenience. Please refresh the page. If the issue persists, contact support at '/dashboard/help'.
context: User reported filter panel issue on mobile

prompt: How do I contact support?
completion: Contact support by clicking the 'Help' icon or visiting '/dashboard/help'.

prompt: Can I filter by traffic and referring domains at the same time?
completion: Absolutely! Use the sliders for Organic Traffic and Referring Domains in the filter panel to set your desired ranges.

prompt: What is the minimum domain rating I can select?
completion: The minimum domain rating is shown on the left end of the Domain Rating slider in the filter panel.

prompt: I want to see only EU websites
completion: Filter by country and select 'EU' or specific European countries in the Country (Traffic) filter.

prompt: How do I leave feedback?
completion: Leave feedback by clicking the 'Feedback' button in the sidebar or visiting '/dashboard/feedback'.

prompt: Your recommendations were not helpful
completion: Thank you for your feedback. Can you tell me more about what you were looking for? I'll try to improve my suggestions.

prompt: Show me all websites with a spam score below 10
completion: Set the Spam Score slider to a maximum of 10 in the filter panel to see those websites.

prompt: How do I navigate to the dashboard?
completion: Click the 'Dashboard' link in the main navigation menu or go to '/dashboard'.

prompt: Can I save my filter settings?
completion: Yes, click the 'Save Filter' button at the bottom of the filter panel.

prompt: What happens if I exclude IPs?
completion: Excluding IPs will remove websites from your results that share IP addresses with domains you already own or have purchased.

prompt: How do I view website details?
completion: Click on any website in the list to view its details, metrics, and available options.

prompt: Can I filter by niche?
completion: Yes, use the 'Allowed Niches' filter to select one or more niches for your search.

prompt: How do I log out?
completion: Click your profile icon in the top right corner and select 'Log Out' from the dropdown menu.

prompt: What is the maximum traffic I can filter for?
completion: The maximum traffic value is shown on the right end of the Organic Traffic slider. Adjust the slider to set your preferred range.

prompt: Can I filter by multiple categories?
completion: Yes, select as many categories as you like in the Category filter. Your results will update automatically.

prompt: How do I add a new group?
completion: Go to '/dashboard/groups' and click 'Add Group'. Enter the group name and save.

prompt: I want to see only websites with permanent articles
completion: Use the Permanent Article price slider to filter for websites offering permanent articles.

prompt: Can I change the language of the interface?
completion: Yes, change the language by selecting your preferred option in the Language dropdown in '/dashboard/settings'.

prompt: Can I delete a website from my account?
completion: Yes, go to '/dashboard/websites', select the website you want to delete, and click the 'Delete' button.

prompt: How do I update my profile information?
completion: To update your profile, visit '/dashboard/settings/profile' and edit your details.

prompt: What payment methods do you accept?
completion: We accept credit cards, PayPal, and bank transfers. You can manage payment options at '/dashboard/billing'.

prompt: Can I get a refund?
completion: Refunds are available within 30 days of purchase. Please contact support via '/dashboard/help' for assistance.

prompt: How do I change my password?
completion: Go to '/dashboard/settings/security' and select 'Change Password'.

prompt: Can I view my billing history?
completion: Yes, your billing history is available at '/dashboard/billing/history'.

prompt: How do I contact the admin?
completion: You can contact the admin by sending a message through '/dashboard/help' or emailing admin@example.com.

prompt: Can I set up two-factor authentication?
completion: Yes, enable two-factor authentication in '/dashboard/settings/security'.

prompt: How do I view notifications?
completion: Notifications are shown in the bell icon at the top right or at '/dashboard/notifications'.

prompt: Can I customize my dashboard layout?
completion: Yes, you can customize your dashboard by dragging and dropping widgets at '/dashboard'.

prompt: How do I invite a team member?
completion: Invite team members by going to '/dashboard/team' and clicking 'Invite Member'.

prompt: Can I set up email alerts for new orders?
completion: Yes, configure email alerts in '/dashboard/settings/notifications'.

prompt: How do I access API documentation?
completion: API documentation is available at '/dashboard/api/docs'.

prompt: Can I change my subscription plan?
completion: Change your subscription plan at '/dashboard/billing/subscription'.

prompt: How do I report a bug?
completion: Report bugs by clicking 'Report Issue' in the sidebar or visiting '/dashboard/help/bug'.

prompt: Can I get a demo of the platform?
completion: Request a demo by filling out the form at '/dashboard/demo'.

prompt: How do I view analytics for my websites?
completion: View website analytics at '/dashboard/websites/analytics'.

prompt: Can I set up custom filters?
completion: Yes, create and save custom filters in the filter panel or at '/dashboard/filters'.

prompt: How do I access the help center?
completion: Access the help center at '/dashboard/help'.

prompt: Can I undo a recent action?
completion: Some actions can be undone. Check for an 'Undo' button or visit '/dashboard/activity' to review recent actions.
